title: Donde Voy
lyrics: All alone I have started my journey  to the darkness of darkness I go With a reason, I stopped for a moment  in this world full of pleasure so frail Town after town on I travel,  pass through faces I know and know not Like a bird in flight, sometimes I topple. Time and time again, just farewells Donde voy, donde voy.  Day by day, my story unfolds Solo estoy, solo estoy.  All alone as the day I was born
